rate prices and is based on a sampling\nalgorithm that performs approximate selection with limited communication,\nleading again to asymptotically optimal communication. Our results do not\nrequire any prior knowledge on the agents' valuations, and mainly follow from\nnatural sampling techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 22:30:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-26"}
