mpered with. The experimental results\nshow that the proposed method improves the accuracy by 2.12%-7.12% compared\nwith state-of-the-art methods under the public database Carioca, New Spanish.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2022 08:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-26"}
