 transition layer acts as a discontinuity, separating the\npair plasma from the ambient plasma. Such a discontinuity is an important\nbuilding block for astrophysical pair plasma jets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Aug 2022 13:15:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-26"}
